commits.sourceNew: /** * Processes the given {@link ExtensionQuery} and returns a corresponding * {@link Query} instance. Subclasses must either return a {@link Query} * instance or raise a {@link ParseException}. This method must not return * null. * * @param query * the extension query * @return a new query instance * @throws ParseException * if the query can not be parsed. */ public abstract Query parse(final ExtensionQuery query) throws ParseException;
